---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Neurosage Hub"
  description="Privacy Policy for Neurosage Hub, operated by Learning Source, LLC."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-10">Updated: August 18, 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">

      <p>Neurosage Hub, operated by <strong>Learning Source, LLC</strong> ("Learning Source," "Neurosage Hub," "us," "we," or "our"), operates the website <a href="https://neurosagehub.com" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">https://neurosagehub.com</a> (the "Service").</p>

      <p>This Privacy Policy informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service and the choices you have associated with that data. We use your data to provide and improve the Service. By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">Definitions</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 list-none pl-0">
        {[
          ['Service', 'Access to and use of https://neurosagehub.com, the Neurosage Hub platform operated by Learning Source, LLC, and any associated products and services.'],
          ['Personal Data', 'Data about a living individual who can be identified from those data (alone or with other information in our possession).'],
          ['Usage Data', 'Data collected automatically, either generated by the use of the Service or from the Service infrastructure itself (e.g., duration of a page visit).'],
          ['Cookies', 'Small files stored on your device (computer or mobile).'],
          ['Data Controller', 'Determines the purposes and means of processing personal information. For this policy, Learning Source, LLC is the Data Controller.'],
        ].map(([term, def]) => (
          <li class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-gray-100">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">{term}:</span> {def}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">Information Collection and Use</h2>
      <p>We collect several types of information to provide and improve our Service, including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li>Name (first and last)</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Phone number</li>
        <li>Address (street, city, state/province, postal code)</li>
        <li>Cookies and Usage Data</li>
        <li>IP address, browser type/version, pages visited, time/date of visit</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">Use of Data</h2>
      <p>We use collected data to provide and maintain our Service, notify you of changes, provide customer support, analyze and improve functionality, monitor usage, and share relevant offers (unless you opt out).</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">Cookies &amp; Tracking</h2>
      <p>We use cookies, beacons, tags, and scripts to track activity and store preferences. You can set your browser to refuse cookies, though some features may not function properly without them.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">Legal Basis (GDPR)</h2>
      <p>If you are from the EEA, we process your Personal Data under contract performance, your consent, our legitimate business interests, or legal obligations.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">California Privacy Rights (CCPA)</h2>
      <p>California residents may request details regarding our disclosure of personal information to third parties for marketing purposes. Email us at <a href="mailto:info@neurosagehub.com" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">info@neurosagehub.com</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain Personal Data only as long as necessary to fulfill this Privacy Policy's purposes or comply with law.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">Security of Data</h2>
      <p>We use commercially acceptable safeguards to protect your Personal Data, but no method of online transmission or storage is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our Service is not directed to anyone under 18. We do not knowingly collect data from minors. If we become aware of such collection, we will remove it promptly.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes are effective once posted on this page.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Learning Source, LLC</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:info@neurosagehub.com" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">info@neurosagehub.com</a></p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
